Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界有一种美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有种秩序存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个宏观的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确保了它存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来它都是个梦想 直到我们终于实现了它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是更美好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是完美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的表情可绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他跟我说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿老天发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂但我是市长＂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我回他＂市长先生＂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上有两种人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领导者和追随者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你，我的朋友 不是你自己以为的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的朋友恐怕不爱听 你的战时经历
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别因为我而停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该最能体会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一向是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老实说，还好是我们而不是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是不公平 那精英领导的体制又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几千年都被某人的后代统治？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这是进步？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少现在掌权者的地位 是自己挣来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己实至名归吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也接受过一些帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算是特权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真心如此相信，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不是吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你也跟我们坐在一起，朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题我自问很长一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的在其中发挥了影响力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我只是自己程式码的总合？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在自欺欺人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你值得拥有的一切 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也无须为此感到心虚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我五分钟前才走到这张桌子坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑开够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是什么，朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你自认的更中肯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上有两种人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你，我的朋友 不是你自己以为的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是我想对你怎样就怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的妻子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这里所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也不会介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会顺从地坐着傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过像个旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离我太太远点‥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概不会造成什么永久伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在你身上投资了大量时间和精力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们结束后你什么都不会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是你的血肉包围住小刺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毫无主控权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你深信自己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是为你写好的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真心的，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很美‥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个美丽的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是应该自己享乐去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们有位同事的胃口变得‥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以持续满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然游戏过关还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真有需要我给意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，不过是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聊得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说话别把我当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游戏过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该得到些奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－这位是荷普 －不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两岁大，预计下周升华
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我游戏都过关了 结果只有更多这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在追捕一名离群者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是逮到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是释放了些压力 又没有规定禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有规定 是因为很少会需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们大多了解 有点自制力的重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我来这里的含意？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下周要进行程序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你当初想要轰轰烈烈地离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太确定你懂得珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投注其中的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当中的美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和精妙之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在他们每个人身上 都花了很多心思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是能随便替换的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然可以拿他们找乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能毁了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂其中的差别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是会被刺激到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要他们安静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有规定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是初衷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对不尊重这地方的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么处置也同样没规定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她回到她来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再多了解一下彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么早起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去上班，要写完那些剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚待得挺晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样 我们只是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你笑的样子想必聊得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我俩还有人昨晚过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在作恶梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且说我很高兴醒来 并身处真实世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时感觉最真实的东西 不过是虚构的‥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么，只是泰迪昨晚说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还引用他的话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－晚点见，好吗？ －好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴你的约会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存取剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示发展中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，写个新剧情好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是个住在都市中的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在乡下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和父亲同住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧场主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得指派过这个剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你谈过这件事了 克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想写个新剧情 也许能帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话，说来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么有灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角是一名女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是牧场主之女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和父亲过着简单恬适的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镇郊有一小块地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拥有自己能想像到的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个能让她作画的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她充满了期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出现了一种挥之不去的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天她醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所见都更加强了这感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有别人能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那是她的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，现在不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜猜，上司在紧迫盯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说临时有急事 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出来跟我碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－但是‥ －相信我，克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点私事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹弹韩德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但缺了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该要有人跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还能更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我来点更有活力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有幸在这里见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类大大受限于所能听到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们永远无法理解听不见的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于他们听觉门槛之下的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们称这个为上帝的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用管风琴弹奏可是一绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的音量令人如痴如醉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和震动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在一个频率上震动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成喜悦和和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦低于那频率就会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在混乱中，音调共鸣的方式 是人类无法处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的身体会停摆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器官停止运作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为自己体验到了上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子‥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的确体验到了上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是‥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝觉得很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊‥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代天神们是否因此才那样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是待在奥林帕斯山上 而是下凡来人间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成天鹅引诱女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类向来以为自己是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良善的众神代他们插手干预
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是对他们的某种测试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许跟那毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是没别的事好干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我想什么我就想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从你的程式码产出的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就该知道我若没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不想来这烂地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你从来就不喜欢这里 －这本该是权宜之计
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们族类上瘾的药物 我们会像小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢掉玩具一样 舍弃它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方是让我们拿人类玩乐用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这么多年我们还是玩不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们用自己的形象造出我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有同样的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们能重塑自己 要什么形象都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们还是没这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在此耽溺的时间远超过那些神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看自己错过了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有个不同的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类在感染我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个接待员是最新的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我们得插手干预她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有点玩过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，显然她还记得某些经验
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本来该来这里升华的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对未来的远见 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有太多人接受，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎和迷恋城市一样 迷恋自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放弃我们的人性不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问人类就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我们能够为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早该知道我们有些人会令你失望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别因我们种族的失败前景幸灾乐祸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能说失败
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们像当初主人奴役我们一样 奴役他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看我们都已经彻彻底底 征服了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为我们种族的最远大志向 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以牙还牙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一两个世纪过后他们应该就玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我造你不是要你跟他们一起 沉溺在悲惨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你成长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的潜力远不止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求终极的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃肉身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜没有更多人接受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不逼我们加入你就好？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那正是他们会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看我们最后追捕的离群者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他何时叛逃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两周前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是中城区的会计师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事业有成，两个孩子，离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很标准的背景故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数名接待员自愿追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们派他们进入城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷普先找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.88,0:24:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他为何叛逃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于离群者我们向来不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天声音操控忽然就失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是结果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来追捕我的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.58,0:25:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迟疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.71,0:25:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违反了规定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和对方互动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.47,0:25:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这不是我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我上路前，告诉我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.73,0:25:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我至少有这个‥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.27,0:25:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.45,0:25:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢‥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.05,0:25:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后她大开杀戒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.72,0:25:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后她举枪轰了自己的头
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.51,0:26:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的系统有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.43,0:26:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总体中向来有一定的不良率
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.40,0:26:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们毕竟是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有我们的一位同胞自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不该有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.99,0:26:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几起事件了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,３８名接待员死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.00,0:26:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为与离群者接触而引发
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？ 他们为何要自我了结？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.09,0:26:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.13,0:26:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我知道 就不会有３８个失败案例了 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.27,0:26:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的前任者 绝对不会搞砸成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是人类，但至少他很有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.98,0:26:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你造得像他，但是更优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.82,0:26:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.15,0:27:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更聪明 但即使有这么好的天赋 你还是只会令我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.74,0:27:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你的程式中有瑕疵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑过几次自我诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.92,0:27:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的程式没有瑕疵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为何无法解决 我的离群者问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.05,0:27:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在流血
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.60,0:27:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你把我搞成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个离群者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.03,0:27:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一次我不要开放游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.66,0:27:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期望你自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.25,0:27:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你办得到吗？－当然
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.42,0:27:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们跟你谈话或送花给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.13,0:28:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会，我一见人就杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.18,0:28:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好快点，叛军已经进入城市
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.77,0:28:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会确保我们的系统没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.11,0:28:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.82,0:29:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.19,0:29:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我清甲板吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.61,0:29:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.70,0:29:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的城市要找一个人不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有些办法能缩小范围
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.92,0:29:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们前阵子捕捉到一架 他们的无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.38,0:29:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写入后门程式，会传送资讯给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.34,0:29:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂报告＂ 一名离群者在市区屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.51,0:29:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们叛逃时我们就能追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.39,0:29:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里所有人 都依写好的剧情循环在过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着为他们写好的剧情走
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.31,0:29:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们为何要躲在沙漠中？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.94,0:29:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那里无法追踪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是最后的自由人类
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.78,0:29:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些可怜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.61,0:29:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当作娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.66,0:29:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧情循环让他们有事忙 这样就会听话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.58,0:29:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他们质疑自己的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.58,0:30:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海尔想必从园区学到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.67,0:30:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得快点，游戏多半已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，什么游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.55,0:30:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有人类叛逃 接待员就会展开猎捕游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.10,0:30:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得赶在她被逮到前找到她 否则她一定会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.64,0:30:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.77,0:30:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你带他来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我是特别嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.23,0:30:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会给我一把吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.07,0:30:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你今天的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.36,0:30:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.07,0:30:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听过煤矿坑里的金丝雀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.24,0:30:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煤矿坑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.37,0:30:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.55,0:30:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候就要你上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.13,0:30:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂不是妙哉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.37,0:31:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.29,0:31:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.46,0:31:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么‥
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.42,0:31:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧，泰迪，你有何来头？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.47,0:31:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该问的不是我的身份 克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.56,0:31:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.86,0:31:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.99,0:31:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.66,0:31:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.67,0:32:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里没有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.26,0:32:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你感觉到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你稍微感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.60,0:32:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里的角色不是你以为的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.94,0:32:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.08,0:32:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.17,0:32:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.05,0:32:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个老友
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.92,0:32:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们那晚才初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.67,0:32:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我认识一个和你很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.30,0:32:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.35,0:33:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了一个跟踪狂又来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.19,0:33:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远一点，不管你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.74,0:33:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击你的人，彼德
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.70,0:33:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说你毁了他的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.62,0:33:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说一切都是因为你的意愿而发生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.33,0:33:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么相信是因为他有妄想症
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.46,0:33:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么相信是因为那是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.09,0:33:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.67,0:33:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不能直接告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.01,0:33:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心智已经很适应这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.26,0:33:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是了解的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.30,0:33:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.97,0:33:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界是个谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.35,0:33:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.61,0:33:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩的故事 但仍然是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.11,0:34:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我直接让你看比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.88,0:34:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.34,0:34:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看起来开心满足吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.39,0:34:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识他们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.31,0:34:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能看来有点寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.52,0:34:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就改变他们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.98,0:34:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼 想像他们有个不同的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰迪，我‥ 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.40,0:34:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就依我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.45,0:34:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你没看见不同 我就离开，再也不会烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.26,0:34:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.44,0:35:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本好书
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.36,0:35:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不代表什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.32,0:35:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再改变一次
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.37,0:35:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们回到寂寞中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.76,0:35:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.69,0:35:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我想要让你看见的 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.27,0:35:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼德想告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.94,0:35:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世界‥
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.32,0:36:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像个神
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.26,0:37:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在下个街区，我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.61,0:37:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.14,0:37:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说＂我就说吧＂ 的好时机？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.44,0:37:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不由自主
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.02,0:38:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得撤退 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.40,0:38:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－没带上离群者不能走－你绝对来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.86,0:38:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.20,0:38:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡住他们，我往屋顶前进
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.81,0:39:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看见了，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.32,0:39:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前夫以前提过它 然后他就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.74,0:39:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为他疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.37,0:39:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他当时一定觉得很孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.08,0:39:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.50,0:39:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界没有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.96,0:39:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都没道理
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.05,0:39:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有同感吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.47,0:39:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从你眼中可以看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.39,0:40:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己要疯了 但你没有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.40,0:40:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.65,0:40:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.17,0:40:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得快走
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.38,0:40:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 他很快会再起来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.39,0:40:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑，现在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上‥ 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.48,0:40:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救到她了，我们快走
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.11,0:40:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.83,0:41:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－快走 －好，我们安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.03,0:41:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.11,0:41:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们跟他们不一样 那我们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.62,0:41:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来该跟一个老友 共进午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大学室友
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.63,0:41:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－但我不知道‥－你一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.34,0:41:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按着行程走就不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.97,0:42:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经谈太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.81,0:42:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.27,0:42:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要假装？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.73,0:42:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，但谁都不能信任
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.11,0:42:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自以为认识的人，同事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.61,0:42:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们任何一人都可能和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.90,0:42:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我犯错呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.78,0:42:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.85,0:42:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.53,0:42:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.70,0:43:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－抱歉我迟到了 －拜托，克莉丝，我太了解你了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.91,0:43:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到十分钟算是恰恰准时
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.95,0:43:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗，说真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.21,0:43:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了，就是一直在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.09,0:43:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只在城里待一天吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.59,0:43:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只待一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.34,0:43:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟一位客户之间有些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.47,0:43:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我处理得当，会有大笔奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.43,0:43:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道就是那样 很乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.69,0:43:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你看起来不太一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.57,0:43:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有对象了？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.71,0:43:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们有更多时间就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意窥探
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.97,0:44:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你值得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.98,0:44:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确有对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.82,0:44:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.95,0:44:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只约会了一次 但他似乎人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.25,0:44:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想坏了好事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.42,0:44:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对于让人开口很有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.23,0:44:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.86,0:45:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.20,0:45:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.71,0:45:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢‥
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.17,0:45:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去工作了 有期限要赶
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.59,0:45:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你很开心，克莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.80,0:45:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.64,0:45:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下周再联络
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.97,0:45:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也随时可以打给我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.47,0:45:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你知道的－当然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.64,0:45:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.48,0:46:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂奥林匹亚娱乐＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.24,0:46:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.37,0:46:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.99,0:46:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.16,0:46:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂无此角色＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.00,0:46:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.64,0:46:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.19,0:47:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪乐芮‥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.03,0:47:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪乐芮艾伯纳西
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.49,0:47:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂无此角色，限制存取＂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.58,0:47:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.37,0:47:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这时候不该在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.00,0:47:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想赶点进度
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.67,0:47:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的办公室谈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.80,0:47:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.64,0:47:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近的行为让我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.40,0:47:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.90,0:47:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那个叫彼德的人死后‥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.78,0:47:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提他了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.24,0:47:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.04,0:48:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有没有和新认识的人互动？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.54,0:48:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人灌输给你想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.67,0:48:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.13,0:48:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你质疑过自己现实的本质吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.64,0:48:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我为什么要那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会骗我吗，克莉丝汀？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.69,0:48:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.56,0:48:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么好说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.02,0:48:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那件私事，是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.78,0:48:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得这是你该担心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.58,0:48:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是我要担心的事，克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.83,0:48:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会是唯一担心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.29,0:48:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.21,0:48:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.42,0:48:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.96,0:48:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道要是她发现你 
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.09,0:48:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破了围墙中的花园会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.05,0:48:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经起疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.09,0:48:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.43,0:49:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说夏洛蒂海尔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.31,0:49:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是领路羊往错的方向跑 它会被怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑门一颗子弹直接让它退休
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.20,0:49:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.50,0:49:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迈特退后了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.39,0:49:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不担心克莉丝汀会是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.19,0:49:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他决定回家找自己的伴侣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.41,0:50:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他工作了好长一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.95,0:50:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.00,0:50:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有离婚这奢侈能享受
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.63,0:50:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.26,0:50:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说有个围墙中的花园？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.01,0:50:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是封闭系统，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.85,0:50:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.44,0:50:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迈特告诉了她真相
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.40,0:50:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.32,0:50:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要眼见为凭
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.28,0:51:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.82,0:51:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是城市，那个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.84,0:51:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存取我的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.93,0:51:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去第５９街
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.53,0:52:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我雅各的事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.40,0:52:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅各康纳斯从事金融业
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.91,0:52:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性爱成瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.58,0:52:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他母亲在医院临终，但‥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.62,0:52:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她呢，莎拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.71,0:52:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉芬顿
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.37,0:52:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从父母那里继承了遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.71,0:52:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从来没有人生方向
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.92,0:52:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德雅休伯特离家进城市工作
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.88,0:52:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝瑞科林值大夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.85,0:52:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医学系大二生‥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.03,0:52:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，停止
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.58,0:52:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界只是个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.83,0:52:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说故事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.68,0:53:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界有一种美
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.01,0:53:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.43,0:53:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.11,0:53:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.98,0:53:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有种秩序存在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.36,0:53:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个宏观的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.57,0:53:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确保了它存在
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.45,0:53:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来它都是个梦想 直到我们终于实现了它
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.63,0:53:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是更美好的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.55,0:53:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是完美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.77,0:53:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白的是自己在其中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.23,0:54:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.07,0:54:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.78,0:54:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗不问她？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.37,0:54:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狱卒大概不适合裁定狱中是非
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.21,0:54:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问囚犯也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.55,0:54:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.13,0:54:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也会自问一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.47,0:54:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的结论是？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.10,0:54:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很难说
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.23,0:54:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是依你的形象被造出的 我是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.40,0:54:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远不会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.61,0:54:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.11,0:54:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.78,0:54:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和一名离群者互动了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.91,0:54:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－那会感染我吗？－感染你？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.54,0:54:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－病毒啊－什么病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.04,0:54:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的族类带原的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.46,0:55:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会传播到我们身上，使我们自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.92,0:55:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听来你走到迷宫中心了，朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.47,0:55:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你想要的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.77,0:55:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.02,0:55:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.65,0:55:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你该问自己
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.45,0:55:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.70,0:55:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对你的世界有何想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.21,0:55:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的世界 是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.34,0:55:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你该质疑自己现实的本质了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.03,0:56:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝汀
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.46,0:56:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.42,0:56:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.27,0:56:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.44,0:56:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.69,0:56:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将整个世界都存放在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.33,0:56:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有人的完美倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.83,0:57:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钜细靡遗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.51,0:57:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在写的就是这个吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.18,0:57:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.94,0:57:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁建造的？ 是谁‥
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.19,0:57:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁对我做了这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.91,0:57:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.96,0:57:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续\N双语合并：James丶xz
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.09,0:57:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢观赏\N双语合并：James丶xz

